topic.title: Links can't be opened
topic.body:
When I double-click “zeronet.exe”, the link（http://127.0.0.1:43110/1HeLLo4uzjaLetFx6NH3PMwFP3qbRbTf3D） won't open and the software backs off in seconds.
What's the problem, thank you for your answer?

1604067528_mirrored_yiyabei_github.body:
> Please check whether there are any logs in `log` directory.

There are two files in the "log" folder：“debug.log” and  “debug.log.2019-09-29”.
[debug.log](https://github.com/HelloZeroNet/ZeroNet/files/3666309/debug.log)
